 "remarks": "Beautifully updated contemporary-style Raised Ranch offering approximately 2,650 square feet, four bedrooms, and three full baths in a desirable Wilton location. Recent improvements include a newly renovated kitchen, refinished flooring throughout, fresh interior paint, new carpeting in the lower level, and new A/C wall units.  The main level features soaring ceilings throughout the living and dining areas, creating a bright, open, and airy atmosphere filled with natural light. A flexible floor plan offers multiple living spaces and generously sized rooms, providing plenty of options for everyday living, entertaining, or working from home.  Additional highlights include two fireplaces, a spacious deck, a detached one-car garage, and ample additional parking. Set on a peaceful 2.13-acre property while remaining convenient to Wilton Center, shopping, dining, parks, commuter routes, and train access.",
